  wmclockmon-0.7.2.ebuild: Stable on x86.
  wmclockmon-0.3.0.ebuild, wmclockmon-0.4.0.ebuild, wmclockmon-0.5.0.ebuild:
  Remove old versions...

  13 Apr 2004; Don Seiler <rizzo@gentoo.org>; wmclockmon-0.3.0.ebuild,
  wmclockmon-0.4.0.ebuild, wmclockmon-0.5.0.ebuild, wmclockmon-0.7.2.ebuild:
